| Phase         | Step                        | Instructions | Description                                                                            |
+---------------+-----------------------------+--------------+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| Compile/Link  |                             | 14,685       | After all functions are compiled and linked into a single design                       |
|               |                             |              |                                                                                        |
| Unroll/Inline |                             |              | After user unroll and inline pragmas are applied                                       |
|               | (1) unroll                  | 93,524       | user unroll pragmas are applied                                                        |
|               | (2) simplification          | 36,537       | simplification of applied user unroll pragmas                                          |
|               | (3) inline                  | 28,910       | user inline pragmas are applied                                                        |
|               | (4) simplification          | 24,383       | simplification of applied user inline pragmas                                          |
|               |                             |              |                                                                                        |
| Array/Struct  |                             |              | After user array partition and struct aggregate/disaggregate pragmas are applied       |
|               | (1) array partition         | 19,581       | user array partition pragmas are applied                                               |
|               | (2) simplification          | 19,207       | simplification of applied user array partition & struct aggregate/disaggregate pragmas |
|               | (3) aggregate/disaggregate  | 19,315       | user struct aggregate/disaggregate pragmas are applied                                 |
|               | (4) array reshape           | 27,080       | apply array reshape pragmas                                                            |
|               | (5) access patterns         | 22,216       | array access pattern optmizations                                                      |
|               |                             |              |                                                                                        |
| Performance   |                             |              | After transformations are applied to meet performance pragma targets                   |
|               | (1) loop simplification     | 21,327       | loop and instruction simplification                                                    |
|               | (2) parallelization         | 23,663       | loops are unrolled or pipelined to meet performance targets                            |
|               | (3) array partition         | 23,187       | arrays are partitioned to meet performance targets                                     |
|               | (4) simplification          | 23,187       | simplification of design after performance transformations                             |
|               |                             |              |                                                                                        |
| HW Transforms |                             |              | After hardware transfomations                                                          |
|               | (1) lowering                | 21,517       | initial conversion to HW specific instructions                                         |
|               | (2) optimizations           | 22,182       | high level synthesis optimizations                                                     |
